Timedatectl set-timezone

HOSTNAME: 
Hostnamectl set-hostname <nazwa_hostname>
nano /etc/hosts

SSH:
apt install openssh-server
nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
PermitRootLogin yes
sudo systemctl restart ssh


FIREWALLD:
